title: Fox News interviews 'Swedish national security advisor'

organizations.name: swedish defense ministry and foreign office

text: show ad Sweden ridicules Fox News after Bill O'Reilly interviews 'country's national security advisor' - but the government has no idea who he is Fox News commentator Bill O'Reilly interviewed 'Swedish defense and national security advisor' identified as Nils Bildt about immigration and crime on-air But security experts in Sweden said he wasn't a familiar figure in their ranks Swedish Defense Ministry and Foreign Office said they knew nothing of him Incident comes a week after President Donald Trump alluded to a security threat in Sweden during a rally on February 18 But there hadn't been any major incident in Sweden on the previous night
